5
00:00:10,326 --> 00:00:12,739
Davvero? Beh, magari dovrei...

6
00:00:12,767 --> 00:00:14,978
inquadrare la questione diversamente.

7
00:00:14,979 --> 00:00:16,540
Terry, lei nota qualcosa?

8
00:00:17,909 --> 00:00:19,109
Amy?

9
